                    </p>
                    
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <img src="https://hubcoapp-images.s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/pb/emails/footer.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 165px; display: block;outline: 0; border: 0;">
